#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
"""
考勤排班数据分析 - 独立可运行脚本
=====================================
将 attendance-pipeline 的完整流程（清洗→指标计算→透视分析→HTML报告→同比对比）
打包为单文件 Python 脚本，下载即可运行。

用法:
    python attendance_pipeline.py all --workspace D:\\path\\to\\workspace --roster-index 15
    python attendance_pipeline.py all-with-compare --workspace ... --prev-workspace ...
    python attendance_pipeline.py clean --workspace ... --roster-index 15
    python attendance_pipeline.py metrics --workspace ...
    python attendance_pipeline.py pivot --workspace ...
    python attendance_pipeline.py report --workspace ...
    python attendance_pipeline.py render --workspace ...
    python attendance_pipeline.py compare --workspace ... --prev-workspace ...
    python attendance_pipeline.py inject --workspace ...
    python attendance_pipeline.py quick-report --workspace ...

输入文件（放在 --workspace 目录或默认 Downloads 文件夹）:
    - 原始数据.xlsx (必填)
    - 离职流程.xlsx
    - 花名册 (N).xlsx
    - 班次.xlsx
    - 补签管理.xlsx
    - 美区签字报表 (2).xlsx / (1).xlsx / .xlsx

依赖: pandas, numpy, openpyxl
      pip install pandas numpy openpyxl
"""
